messages.text:
I cannot help it but I still miss u. I hate myself for being like this. U really hurt me a lot. It is really painful. And I felt more painful after just now. I really do see a future, but u r the one that is not willing to try. It’s not about giving chance or not, it’s about u not wanting to have a future w me. U find it tiring isn’t it. U have no trust in me n u dw urself to get hurt in the future. 
I’m sadden by the fact that the only reason for u willing to try again is to have skinship w me. U gave in to ur desire n u weren’t using ur brain. U said u use ur brain to think instead of ur heart. Then why did u text me in the morning. Why did u stop me from leaving the bed. Why did u give me hope and back out. U used me n u regret abt it. I was fine despite being very sad, until u said u can no longer accept me regardless of what I do. My heart broke again. i really hope I can act like u, thinking rationally. U r so mean to me and my brain is telling me u r rlly not worth it, but my heart is not letting go. 

Im conflicted about my decision to stay. It isn’t about the difference in ideology, it’s about how I’m not wanted in this rls. U only need me for ur needs now. U don’t include me in ur future anymore. Do u know how disappointed I was just now; I feel like I’m not appreciated. U wanted me to appreciate about everything I had. I would have to appreciate myself first, n that’s why I left. U made me trust u n back out. I really wanted to get back to u and I really thought a lot about our problem. I don’t find ideology a big Issue, and the reason why we always quarreled were because I took advantage of ur “love” towards me. And I wanted more attention from u. But i did it in a wrong way. I thought u were fine w my nonsense. Afterall i over estimated it. My actions don’t necessarily represent what I’m truly thinking, including my view of life. I think I showed too much negative emotions and sides about me, that u no longer find me attractive and U r tired of staying by my side. I was so confident that similar conflict wouldn’t happen again, as I will be more mature and act rationally with u so that u won’t become tired and stress about me again. I wanted a loving rls too, where both parties can motivate each other to do well. But I realised that it’s no longer about me; If I’m willing to change or solve the problem together. It’s about u, ur trust in our love, and u r not willing to to have a future tgt. U alr had negative impression about me. Udw urself to be hurt. (If differing views was really the true reason why u dw to stay)

U wanted a plan, but what plan do u exactly want to hear. I really have no idea. I wanted to show u my changes w my actions, so that u can change ur mind with time and feel love by me. I will stop finding fault at u. I thought the way we communicated was key as back then I didnt really listen to what u said. I only cared about myself, i thought u would always listen to me. And that’s why conflict occur. I didn’t put myself in ur shoe, in other sense I didn’t bother about ur feeling and despite knowing that U r unhappy, i still proceed to make u more unhappy. I wanted to attract ur attention, hence behaving in such a childish manner. I assured u that that’s not going to happen again , but u have no trust in me isn’t it, u underestimated what u mean to me. But do u know that I’m also a person that likes to improve myself constantly. I was just too comfortable with u and too depress about my current way of life( my roomie and quarreling w u, and meeting only u everyday) that I felt lazy about it. I also want to change it. I want to connect and stay in touch w more people. I wanted my life to be meaningful.  We r definitely not fully incompatible, i enjoy playing games too, it’s just I don’t have a laptop for me to play league. i work hard for exam too. At least previously, when we just started dating, u see me studying seriously in my room tho I may procrastinate awhile, but I still do my work seriously. I submited all my assignments on time and I always do it in advance. At least I know what I want to achieve n i try to achieve it. U r too negative about the future with me. 

There are couples that have differing views and they got together, because they are receptive. With the fact that I don’t find us having very differing views, i don’t understand why u kept on insisting that we won’t last long. So I take it as u don’t truly love me for who I am, and U no longer have trust in me. It hurt to think in this way but I think U merely enjoyed the company with me, eg those happy days where watch Netflix n chill. And nowadays when we r pack with our school work, and having conflict frequently, U no longer felt comforted by me. U only miss the feeling and excitement u had with me when we just started dating. This made me very disappointed. U made me fall in love with u and u took it away. Then why did u lie to me. I am really really really hurt. 

I know u did tell me that im causing a lot of stress to u back then, and u r afraid of making me angry. Im really sorry for neglecting those. Now that I realized the seriousness of this issue, i told u that I’m really willing to stop causing all these problem. I thought things would be right but u jus want to end it. R u making any effort to tell me about the real reason, all u said previously were only me causing u a lot of stress and not feeling loved, u didn’t mention about ideology. I was the one who mention it, but I didn’t mean it. But the next time u bring this up, u want a breakup. Is this fair to me:)  I won’t ask to stay w u anymore. I just want to let u know how I feel.
Sorry ye i was buying lunch n eating lunch
Will get back to u asap
How do u feel abt what she sais
the real reason is that I dont see us lasting forever
so i want to end it now
Ye just go for it then min . Dont worry about it
I think its a very valid reason
Thr really is no point staying tgth with someone u dont see yourself wifh in the long term . And if yall r meant to be it will happen
Maybe u cn just reply with a "thank you for taking your time to type all of these .I really appreciate the past few months . I will see you around if i see you Keting" something like this
To just end it off with no animosity
Dont say i love you or what not
